<sect> clrpos
<p>
<descrip>
<tag> Synopsis </tag> Clears position on terminal.
<tag> Syntax </tag>
             <p> clrpos ( <em>row</em>, <em>col</em> )
             <p> clrpos ( <em>row</em> )

<tag> Description </tag>

	<descrip>

	<tag> clrpos ( <em>row</em>, <em>col</em> )</tag>
		clears a position at <em>row</em> and <em>col</em> by printing a space
		there.

	<tag> clrpos ( <em>row</em> )</tag>
		clears a <em>row</em> using a code "clear line" from termcap library.

	</descrip>

	clrpos uses termcap library.

	<tag>See Also</tag> clrscr, mvcrsr, colors.

</descrip>
